metadata.name: Part 3
metadata.description:
Part 3

No Greater Love is not your typical love story. The three photos in this collection are of a man in NYC, showing the distance he takes to escape by doing what he loves.

Later that day, he died of an overdose. I am unaware if it was due to K2 as to what he is smoking in the photos. These are most likely his last recorded moments on earth.
